The "wow" scenario to demo

When you present this, don't click randomly. Walk through a story:

A new cloud migration was completed for a critical payment service.
Several operational alerts have been recorded over the past month.
A regulator has recently emphasized third-party concentration risk.
The AI recommends a Cloud Provider Failure exercise because:
The service hasn't been exercised in 18 months.
Architecture changed significantly.
Previous exercises found communication gaps.
A new critical vendor was introduced.
The workspace automatically:
Identifies affected Business Services.
Selects likely participants.
Suggests meeting times based on availability.
Builds the exercise pack.
Generates objectives, injects, and success criteria.
After the simulated exercise, it generates an After Action Report and an executive presentation outline.

That tells a complete business story in under five minutes.
